# --- Private: research / dev internals. NOT for the public GitHub site. ---
# IMPORTANT: gitignore excludes these from a FRESH `git add` only. It does NOT
# remove them from THIS repo's existing 158-commit history. To publish, create a
# NEW repo from the working tree (see the release steps) so gitignore takes effect
# on the first commit; and ROTATE the Together key first (it is in this history).
# Anchored with a leading slash so the PUBLIC mcp/docs/CLAUDE.md shim is unaffected.
